originalSql:
SELECT 
    a.name AS aka_name,
    t.title AS movie_title,
    p.name AS person_name,
    c.note AS cast_note,
    k.keyword AS movie_keyword,
    ci.kind AS company_type
FROM 
    aka_name a
JOIN 
    cast_info c ON a.person_id = c.person_id
JOIN 
    title t ON c.movie_id = t.id
JOIN 
    movie_keyword mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id
JOIN 
    keyword k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id
JOIN 
    movie_companies mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id
JOIN 
    company_type ci ON mc.company_type_id = ci.id
JOIN 
    name p ON a.person_id = p.imdb_id
WHERE 
    t.production_year >= 2000
ORDER BY 
    t.production_year DESC, a.name

SELECT COALESCE("aka_name"."name", "aka_name"."name") AS "AKA_NAME", "title"."title" AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "name"."name" AS "PERSON_NAME", "cast_info"."note" AS "CAST_NOTE", "keyword"."keyword" AS "MOVIE_KEYWORD", "s1"."kind" AS "COMPANY_TYPE", "title"."production_year"
FROM "aka_name"
INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "cast_info"."person_id"
INNER JOIN "title" ON "cast_info"."movie_id" = "title"."id"
INNER JOIN "movie_keyword" ON "title"."id" = "movie_keyword"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "keyword" ON "movie_keyword"."keyword_id" = "keyword"."id"
INNER JOIN "movie_companies" ON "title"."id" = "movie_companies"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "movie_companies"."company_type_id" = "s1"."id"
INNER JOIN "name" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "name"."imdb_id"
WHERE "title"."production_year" >= 2000
ORDER BY "title"."production_year" DESC NULLS FIRST, "aka_name"."name"

SELECT COALESCE("id", "id") AS "id", "name", "imdb_index", "imdb_id", "gender", "name_pcode_cf", "name_pcode_nf", "surname_pcode", "md5sum"
FROM "name"

SELECT COALESCE("aka_name"."name", "aka_name"."name") AS "AKA_NAME", "title"."title" AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "s1"."name" AS "PERSON_NAME", "cast_info"."note" AS "CAST_NOTE", "keyword"."keyword" AS "MOVIE_KEYWORD", "company_type"."kind" AS "COMPANY_TYPE", "title"."production_year"
FROM "aka_name"
INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "cast_info"."person_id"
INNER JOIN "title" ON "cast_info"."movie_id" = "title"."id"
INNER JOIN "movie_keyword" ON "title"."id" = "movie_keyword"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "keyword" ON "movie_keyword"."keyword_id" = "keyword"."id"
INNER JOIN "movie_companies" ON "title"."id" = "movie_companies"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "company_type" ON "movie_companies"."company_type_id" = "company_type"."id"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "s1"."imdb_id"
WHERE "title"."production_year" >= 2000
ORDER BY "title"."production_year" DESC NULLS FIRST, "aka_name"."name"
